title: L3C North Atlantic Regional (NAR) Sea Surface Temperature (GRIB) - Multimission
summary: NAR product consists in Metop/AVHRR and SNPP/VIIRS derived sub-skin Sea Surface Temperature over North Atlantic and European Seas at 2 km resolution, four times a day.
